                      <h2 data-aos="fade-down" data-aos-duration="2000" data-aos-delay="0">The Nature's - Independent Makers and Growers Market</h2><br>

                      <p style="font-size: 35px; color: greenyellow;">Covid-19 Update</p>
                      <p style="font-size: 18px; color: #d9ffb3;">It is with a heavy heart that we are formally announcing the postponement of The Nature. We had hoped we would have firm date to reschedule to but in light on the ongoing crisis and situation across the world we will have no replacement date to announce. We are determined to make it happen though so watch this space!<p>

                      <p style="font-size: 35px; color: greenyellow;">The Nature's Market</p>
                     <p style="font-size: 18px; color: #d9ffb3;">We’ve been hosting plant swaps for two years and love our wonderful community of plant for fans in Kolkata. We also know that everyone (well us anyway!) have secret wish lists of plants. And however fast folks propagate there are never enough monstera, string of pearls or other special pretties to keep us satisfied.</p>

                <p style="font-size: 35px; color: greenyellow;">Our First Nature's Market</p>
                    <p style="font-size: 18px; color: #d9ffb3;">Sadly our first Plantalia makers and growers market that was scheduled to be on Saturday 25th April 2020 at the fantastic Hagglers Corner, Sheffield is now formally postponed. We are working as hard as we can to find a new date ad we’ll let you know as soon as we have one.</p>
